  "detailed_description": "\"This game represents the abandonment of objects against the arrogance of human beings.\"<br />\r\nShe/it can be inflated to stand up, inflated to float, or deflate air through narrow gaps.<br />\r\nLittle heart pricks your skin and flames.<br />\r\nBecause it will explode her/it.<br />\r\nCollect as many stars as possible during the game.<br />\r\nIt's a very difficult game.<br />\r\nBecause in reality, an inflatable doll can be very difficult to resist.<br />\r\nSo we tried to simulate real life as much as possible.<br />\r\nLet you experience what it's like to be a sex doll.",
  "about_the_game": "\"This game represents the abandonment of objects against the arrogance of human beings.\"<br />\r\nShe/it can be inflated to stand up, inflated to float, or deflate air through narrow gaps.<br />\r\nLittle heart pricks your skin and flames.<br />\r\nBecause it will explode her/it.<br />\r\nCollect as many stars as possible during the game.<br />\r\nIt's a very difficult game.<br />\r\nBecause in reality, an inflatable doll can be very difficult to resist.<br />\r\nSo we tried to simulate real life as much as possible.<br />\r\nLet you experience what it's like to be a sex doll.",
